</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='python'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">h1</span><span class="o">&gt;-&lt;</span><span class="n">em</span><span class="o">&gt;-</span> <span class="n">coding</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">utf_8</span> <span class="o">-&lt;/</span><span class="n">em</span><span class="o">&gt;-&lt;/</span><span class="n">h1</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">Skype4Py</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">time</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">post</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">msg</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">event</span><span class="p">):</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">event</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s">&#39;SENT&#39;</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="n">msg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Body</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s">u&quot;#sendContactRequestToChatMembers&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="n">members</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">msg</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Chat</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Members</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">members</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">__len__</span><span class="p">()):</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="n">members</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Item</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">SetBuddyStatusPendingAuthorization</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">u&quot;auto request&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="n">skype</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Skype4Py</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Skype</span><span class="p">()</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">skype</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OnMessageStatus</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">post</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">skype</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Attach</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="k">while</span> <span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">:</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="n">time</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sleep</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>requestを送りたい人達がいるチャットで#sendContactRequestToChatMembersと発言すれば自動で飛ばされます。
効率的に女の子と仲良くなりたい人も使えると思います。</p>
